string.name: failMessageOnDistance
string.value: The Transporter has given up the mission and went back.

string.name: failMessageOnDie
string.value: Due to the damage on the Transporter, the Delivery Mission has failed.

string.name: say
string.value: Right there! It's the Processing Plant!

string.name: say
string.value: We're not too far from the Processing Plant.

string.name: say
string.value: Please protect us while I refuel!

string.name: say
string.value: Please, quit playing around and protect us!

string.name: say
string.value: Oh! Fueling station! (This can't be a coincidence...)

string.name: say
string.value: We're running out of fuel... It's all over now...

string.name: say
string.value: Darn it! The fuel was leaking!

string.name: say
string.value: I think the aliens have already taken over the route.
